<p>英 /veɪn/    美 /veɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>徒劳的；自负的：</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-vain">in vain</h3>
<p>1.<strong>徒劳；白辛苦：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have tried very hard to find a solution to the problem, but in vain. 
我曾苦苦地探求解决问题的办法，但都是徒劳。</p><footer>2010 江苏</footer></div>

